Paydiamond creative solutions, an e-commerce company into the selling of packages of precious stones said it has introduced a buy now and earn forever, which guarantees subscribers to its service 150% returns on investment (ROP/ROI) in 50weeks. “You can cash out 150% of your investment after 50 weeks duration or you can either cash out both interest and capital after the expiration of 50 weeks or leave your capital for subsequent reinvestment and keep earning for life,”  with the package PayDiamond said in a statement. For more information visit www.paydiamondinc.com. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .